comments: Dinwiddie (DAL) brushes Grimes' (NYK) left arm/front as Grimes turns back toward mid-court and marginal contact occurs.
Powell (DAL) brings his right arm forward slightly and marginal contact occurs with Randle's (NYK) side and left arm as Randle drives into the lane.
Randle (NYK) brings his off-arm outward slightly and marginal contact occurs with Powell's (DAL) side as Randle slows his momentum in the lane.
Robinson (NYK) maintains a rested forearm on Wood's (DAL) back and does not apply any force as Wood elevates to contest the shot attempt.
Wood (DAL) brings his left forearm toward Randle's (NYK) front and marginal contact occurs as Randle elevates for the shot attempt.
Randle's (NYK) off-arm comes forward during the shot attempt and marginal contact occurs with Wood's (DAL) front as Wood contests the shot attempt.
Powell (DAL) establishes himself in Grimes' (NYK) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Randle (NYK) moves somewhat laterally as Wood (DAL) cuts back toward him and marginal body contact occurs as they come together in the lane after Wood's gather.
Powell (DAL) and Robinson (NYK) each make clean contact with the ball as simultaneous incidental arm contact occurs during rebounding.
Powell (DAL) is moving alongside Randle's (NYK) path and marginal body contact occurs as they come together at the end of the drive.
Hardaway Jr. (DAL) brushes Quickley's (NYK) slightly extended off-arm and marginal contact occurs as Quickley dribbles inside the perimeter.
Grimes (NYK) avoids making contact with Doncic's (DAL) right arm and legally contests the jump shot attempt.
Powell (DAL) and McBride (NYK) come together in the lane as the shot attempt is released and marginal body contact occurs prior to McBride losing his balance.
Dinwiddie (DAL) turns slightly prior to marginal contact occurring with Quickley's (NYK) side in the backcourt.
Hardaway Jr. (DAL) brings his hands forward toward Quickley's (NYK) side and marginal contact occurs as Quickley elevates to pass.
Quickley (NYK) releases the pass attempt and the ball crosses half-court within eight seconds.

Wood's (DAL) left forearm comes forward and marginal contact occurs with Randle's (NYK) front as he elevates. Wood then brings his arm down slightly and further marginal contact occurs with Randle's arm after the release of his driving shot attempt.
Grimes (NYK) briefly has his arm around Doncic's (DAL) upper half before correcting.
Hardaway Jr. (DAL) engages and disengages with Quickley (NYK) during the inbound.
Doncic (DAL) and Hardaway Jr. (DAL) each move forward slightly prior to marginal contact occurring with Quickley's (NYK) back and side after Quickley receives the inbound.
Wood (DAL) commits a take foul on McBride (NYK). This contact occurs prior to any initiated by McBride thereafter.
Hardaway Jr.'s (DAL) momentum continues to carry him forward following the pass and marginal contact occurs as he and Randle (NYK) come together along the perimeter.
Doncic (DAL) makes clean contact with the ball and ties Grimes (NYK) up as simultaneous marginal body contact occurs. A jump ball is correctly assessed.
Quickley (NYK) and Hardaway Jr. (DAL) engage with one another and each make clean contact with the ball as simultaneous marginal contact occurs.
Doncic (DAL) legally gains control of the ball after it is touched by another player.
Grimes (NYK) legally contests Hardaway Jr.'s (DAL) jump shot attempt. Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Hardaway Jr.'s (DAL) right leg slightly extends forward and marginal contact occurs with Grimes' (NYK) lower body as Grimes contests the jump shot attempt.
Quickley (NYK) initiates contact with both hands to Doncic's (DAL) back after Doncic gains control of the ball and attempts the put-back.
Ntilikina (DAL) and Randle (NYK) engage and disengage with one another during the inbound.
Doncic (DAL) commits a take foul on McBride (NYK).
Doncic (DAL) inbounds the ball within five seconds.
Powell (DAL) firms up over his right foot and does not deliver illegal contact as he sets the screen on McBride (NYK) during the inbound.
Dinwiddie (DAL) and McBride (NYK) engage and disengage with one another during the inbound.
Dinwiddie (DAL) commits a take foul on McBride (NYK).

Grimes (NYK) commits a take foul on Doncic (DAL). The transition take foul rule does not apply to the last two minutes of either the fourth quarter or overtime. The contact occurs prior to the start of Doncic's upward shooting motion.
McGee (DAL) has a grasp of Robinson's (NYK) right arm and marginal contact occurs as the long rebound falls overhead.
Wood (DAL) and Randle (NYK) each make clean contact with the ball as simultaneous incidental arm contact occurs during rebounding.

Doncic's (DAL) momentum continues to carry him forward as he retrieves the rebound and marginal body contact occurs as he and McBride (NYK) come together during the put-back attempt. Grimes' (NYK) right arm comes forward slightly and marginal contact occurs with Doncic's front simultaneously.
Hardaway Jr. (DAL) legally contests Quickley's (NYK) jump shot attempt.
Wood (DAL) leads with his right leg slightly extended forward and marginal contact occurs with Robinson's (NYK) front as Robinson contests the shot.
Robinson (NYK) initiates arm contact with Wood (DAL) prior to making any contact with the ball during Wood's layup attempt.
Grimes (NYK) establishes himself in Dinwiddie's (DAL) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Dinwiddie (DAL) and Randle (NYK) engage and disengage with one another on the wing.
Wood (DAL) initiates contact with Grimes' (NYK) right arm and affects his driving shot attempt.

Replay review of the foul called on Doncic (DAL) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful. Doncic moves into Robinson (NYK) and delivers contact to Robinson's back that dislodges him from his position during rebounding.
Grimes (NYK) and Wood (DAL) engage and disengage with one another following the pick.
Doncic's (DAL) brings his off-arm forward slightly and marginal contact occurs with Randle's (NYK) front prior to Doncic stepping back from the lane.
Hardaway Jr. (DAL) engages and disengages with Randle (NYK) as Randle moves to set the pick.
Randle (NYK) establishes himself in Dinwiddie's (DAL) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Dinwiddie (DAL) turns slightly prior to marginal side-to-side contact occurring with Quickley (NYK) as Quickley gathers the ball.
Wood (DAL) raises his right arm up and marginal contact occurs with Robinson's (NYK) left hand/wrist as Robinson retrieves the rebound and attempts the subsequent put-back.
Grimes (NYK) and Wood (DAL) engage and disengage with one another as the pick expires.
Randle (NYK) initiates contact with Doncic's (DAL) front and right arm, affecting Doncic's SQBR prior to making contact with the ball at the top of the perimeter.
Wood (DAL) is moving somewhat laterally prior to marginal body contact occurring with McBride (NYK) as McBride drives inside the perimeter.
Randle (NYK) and Doncic (DAL) make incidental arm and body contact with one another during rebounding.
Quickley (NYK) commits a take foul on Dinwiddie (DAL).
Powell (DAL) legally contests Robinson's (NYK) shot attempt near the rim.
McBride (NYK) and Dinwiddie (DAL) engage and disengage with one another as the inbound pass is released.
